      "content": "it’s not about the approach though. i’ve tried everything. every single time i think i’ve found a way out, the loop just resets. it’s like there’s a glitch in who i am. no matter how much 'balance' i find, i just end up right back in this dark spot. it feels like the loop is the only thing that's actually real.",
